I"œ<p>User Authentication is now done in the API Level to ensure Authenticated Approach when working with Proxy API,
Swagger Documentation and Applying Action Parameters to Action Filter.</p>

<h2 id="steps-to-user-authentication">Steps to User Authentication</h2>

<ol>
  <li>Go to APPSeCONNECT Portal&gt; API&gt; Proxy&gt; Click on the AUTHENTICATION button(Top Right Corner) on the APPSeCONNECT Cloud Portal.<br />
<img src="/staticfiles/api-management/media/authentication-proxy.png" alt="authentication-proxy" /></li>
</ol>

<p>2.The following screen appears. Select your User Organisation from the drop-down menu and it will automatically 
generate the Username and Password. <br />
<img src="/staticfiles/api-management/media/authentication-re-generation.png" alt="authentication-re-generation" /></p>

<ol>
  <li>Click on the Re-generate button to regenerate the authentication details as and when required.</li>
</ol>
